{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"30":"Chapters on Drinks"},"section_detail":{"30":{"hadithnumber_first":3371,"hadithnumber_last":3435,"arabicnumber_first":3371,"arabicnumber_last":3435}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3412,"arabicnumber":3412,"text":"Rapporté par ‘Aishah رضي الله عنها : Je préparais trois récipients couverts pour le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) la nuit : un pour son eau d’ablution, un pour son siwak et un pour sa boisson","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":30,"hadith":42}}]}